        "subject": "LU-1126 ldlm: Handle race on transient FLocks with changed mode",
        "message": "LU-1126 ldlm: Handle race on transient FLocks with changed mode\n\nThis patch fixes an issue during overlapping FLocks destroy in\nthe case concerned locks are transient LDLM_FL_TEST_LOCK returned\nwith inverted mode. This a very unlikely+racy situation described\nin LU-1126.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=posix\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I817098f53ff00b1d7de01530e126ddcc2bfab1be\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
